            "chapterTitle": "Prohibition of Bewailing the Deceased",
            "urn": 1624650,
            "body": "<p>Abu Malik Al-Ash'ari (May Allah be pleased with him) said: The Messenger of Allah (\ufdfa) said, \"If the wailing woman does not repent before she dies, she will be made to stand on the Day of Resurrection wearing a garment of pitch and a garment of scabies (Allah knows the nature thereof).\"<br/><br/><b>[Muslim]</b>.<br/><br/></p>",
            "grades": []
